In the early days of south africa when apartheid was on peak an {Indian} origin businessman, {}. He was a visionary and wanted to create a business empire that would be a game-changer in the world of business.
For this he needed a lot of money. Therefore he is planning to host a party for the richest guys in South Africa. Issue is the evil apartheid society is not allowing him to call all the rich guys he knows in the party. 2 persons won't come to the party if even a single person has a difference of k in their complexion. He has a list of n people along with their complexion and money they will invest in his business. He wants to know the maximum money he can get from the party.